":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T14:10:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>會唔會諗多左?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該佢啱<br />\n<br />\n印象中各類聲明，例如反核反戰等<br />\n<br />\n啲名人學者一定響全朵</blockquote><br />\n唔係指班校長唔落名依樣野<br />\n<br />\n才子話&quot;heads&quot;係代表對上仲有人<br />\n但&quot;heads&quot;唔係只一個普通既泛指 指所有學院既領導人咩<br />\n不論係 Principal, Dean, Chancellor 都可以係&quot;heads&quot;<br />\n個人好奇會唔會只係一個簡單既統稱 咩李國寶個啲佢諗太多"},{"pid":"4948094399bc50f26656477644e41fa019266d12","tid":402551,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T14:10:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>會唔會諗多左?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該佢啱<br />\n<br />\n印象中各類聲明，例如反核反戰等<br />\n<br />\n啲名人學者一定響全朵</blockquote><br />\n唔係指班校長唔落名依樣野<br />\n<br />\n才子話&quot;heads&quot;係代表對上仲有人<br />\n但&quot;heads&quot;唔係只一個普通既泛指 指所有學院既領導人咩<br />\n不論係 Principal, Dean, Chancellor 都可以係&quot;heads&quot;<br />\n個人好奇會唔會只係一個簡單既統稱 咩<span style=\"color: red;\">李國章</span>個啲佢諗太多</blockquote>"},{"pid":"da1c8de70fd4a1c7ccb16585b4eadde69f0ebf89","tid":402551,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T14:14:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>會唔會諗多左?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該佢啱<br />\n<br />\n印象中各類聲明，例如反核反戰等<br />\n<br />\n啲名人學者一定響全朵</blockquote><br />\n唔係指班校長唔落名依樣野<br />\n<br />\n才子話&quot;heads&quot;係代表對上仲有人<br />\n但&quot;heads&quot;唔係只一個普通既泛指 指所有學院既領導人咩<br />\n不論係 Principal, Dean, Chancellor 都可以係&quot;heads&quot;<br />\n個人好奇會唔會只係一個簡單既統稱 咩<span style=\"color: red;\">李國章</span>個啲佢諗太多</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n或者，班校長唔想寫明係自己<br />\n揾個含糊字眼填落去就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5281d7cec028bd35a6c557c039ea2eb3ee6961c","tid":402551,"uid":11001,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T14:15:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>會唔會諗多左?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該佢啱<br />\n<br />\n印象中各類聲明，例如反核反戰等<br />\n<br />\n啲名人學者一定響全朵</blockquote><br />\n唔係指班校長唔落名依樣野<br />\n<br />\n才子話&quot;heads&quot;係代表對上仲有人<br />\n但&quot;heads&quot;唔係只一個普通既泛指 指所有學院既領導人咩<br />\n不論係 Principal, Dean, Chancellor 都可以係&quot;heads&quot;<br />\n個人好奇會唔會只係一個簡單既統稱 咩<span style=\"color: red;\">李國章</span>個啲佢諗太多</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n或者，班校長唔想寫明係自己<br />\n揾個含糊字眼填落去就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n根本就係咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70e46a20f82ec79d302e62f647d5bcf45c4db968","tid":402551,"uid":90601,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T14:15:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>會唔會諗多左?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該佢啱<br />\n<br />\n印象中各類聲明，例如反核反戰等<br />\n<br />\n啲名人學者一定響全朵</blockquote><br />\n唔係指班校長唔落名依樣野<br />\n<br />\n才子話&quot;heads&quot;係代表對上仲有人<br />\n但&quot;heads&quot;唔係只一個普通既泛指 指所有學院既領導人咩<br />\n不論係 Principal, Dean, Chancellor 都可以係&quot;heads&quot;<br />\n個人好奇會唔會只係一個簡單既統稱 咩<span style=\"color: red;\">李國章</span>個啲佢諗太多</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n或者，班校長唔想寫明係自己<br />\n揾個含糊字眼填落去就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n事後丸既野......<br />\n全中文媒體都係講緊&quot;校長&quot; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"318fc1803bc1272ee05944bb52e65748a75613c5","tid":402551,"uid":46700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T14:16:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>會唔會諗多左?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該佢啱<br />\n<br />\n印象中各類聲明，例如反核反戰等<br />\n<br />\n啲名人學者一定響全朵</blockquote><br />\n唔係指班校長唔落名依樣野<br />\n<br />\n才子話&quot;heads&quot;係代表對上仲有人<br />\n但&quot;heads&quot;唔係只一個普通既泛指 指所有學院既領導人咩<br />\n不論係 Principal, Dean, Chancellor 都可以係&quot;heads&quot;<br />\n個人好奇會唔會只係一個簡單既統